programs.description:
Rotary in Action follows the diverse social activities of Rotarians in the Philippines. An original concept of Kuya Daniel Razon, the program which is also seen on UNTV 37,  promotes Rotary International's values and principles by featuring the Club's social outreach projects and inspiring the spirit of volunteerism among Filipinos.

Rotary in Action is hosted by Rotarians from the Rotary Club of Kamuning District 3780: Dir. Daniel Razon, PP Gerry Panghulan, PP Romy Roxas, PP Lani Abrenica, PP Dong Lorbes, PP Dondon Tenorio and IPP Efren Capa, with IPP Marilen Lagniton of RC Cubao Edsa and PDG Lyne Abanilla of RI District 3810.<em id="__mceDel" style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;">                                                                                                                                                                           </em>

